</ul>

<hr/>

<h2>ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used</h2>

<ul>
  <li><b>Firebase Authentication</b> for signup, login, and email verification</li>
  <li><b>Firebase Realtime Database</b> for menu data, favorites, cart, profile, and order history</li>
  <li><b>Picasso</b> for efficient image loading from Firebase</li>
  <li><b>Lottie Animations</b> for visual feedback and better user experience</li>
  <li><b>Google Location Services</b> to assist users in filling delivery address</li>
</ul>

<hr/>

<h2>âš™ï¸ Challenges & Learnings</h2>

<p>
While developing this app, managing data flow across multiple sections like menu, favorites, cart, and order history was challenging.
Handling these interactions through adapter-based architecture required careful debugging and restructuring.
</p>

<p>
Another challenge was ensuring the correct data was retrieved and displayed without crashes.
Through continuous testing and refinement, these issues were resolved, resulting in a stable and smooth experience.
</p>

